node.text: “Disney Enchantment,” the brand-new nighttime spectacular coming to Magic Kingdom Park as part of the 50th Anniversary of @WaltDisneyWorld Resort, will not only feature dazzling fireworks and beloved Disney music, but also a new original song from GRAMMY Winner Philip Lawrence. ✨🏰🎶 Here’s a look at the recording of “You Are the Magic,” and head over to the Disney Parks Blog (link in bio) to read more. #DisneyWorld50

node.title: New Original Song, “You Are the Magic” Coming to Disney Enchantment

node.text: With “The World’s Most Magical Celebration” just weeks away, @WaltDisneyWorld cast members are honoring a decades-long tradition with new 50th-themed nametags featuring a dazzling EARidescent design. The shimmering gold accents, iridescent overlay and 50th anniversary logo perfectly represent the splendor of the 18-month celebration, and how our cast members are the heart of it all. To read more, visit the Disney Parks Blog (link in bio). #DisneyWorld50

node.title: New 50th Anniversary EARidescent Cast Member Nametags Distributed

node.text: With “The World’s Most Magical Celebration” just weeks away, @WaltDisneyWorld cast members are honoring a decades-long tradition with new 50th-themed nametags featuring a dazzling EARidescent design. The shimmering gold accents, iridescent overlay and 50th anniversary logo perfectly represent the splendor of the 18-month celebration, and how our cast members are the heart of it all. To read more, visit the Disney Parks Blog (link in bio). #DisneyWorld50

node.text: Check out this sneak peek of the “Light” product range from the EPCOT Light & Color Collection, an exclusive line of merchandise coming to Creations Shop! The assortment of futuristic gear was inspired by the historic transformation of EPCOT and will debut on Sept. 15 when Creations Shop and Club Cool officially opens to guests. In the same way that Disney Imagineers implemented color, materials and light throughout the design of Creation Shop, the EPCOT Light & Color Collection explores the story of EPCOT through the whimsical application of light, the playful use of bold color and iconic EPCOT landmarks and characters. Check back here on the Disney Parks Blog and follow #DisneyWorld50 on social media for regular updates on all the exciting things coming as part of “The World’s Most Magical Celebration”! And stay tuned for more details about Creations Shop and a first look at the range of “Color” products.
